author: Minecraft
description:
We’ve heard your plea for even more cuteness, and now it’s time to level up our baby mobs and go all in on cuteness overload!
Join our very giggly Game Director Agnes Larsson and Game Artist Sarah Boeving as they present our brand‑new baby mob variants. Discover how baby mobs now have their own models and sounds, why going from two pixels to one makes a huge difference, and what a “headfooter” is and how it inspired the creation of tiny baby chicklets. Get ready for adorable, fluffy, and cuddly mobs, find your very own baby mob, craft a name tag, and enjoy cuteness all day long!

Read more here: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/first-features-minecraft-cutest-drop-yet
title: THE CUTEST DROP YET!
